```
**Root Cause:** Argo Rollouts CRDs not installed before Helm chart deployment.

### 🔧 FIX:
```bash
# Install Argo Rollouts first (CRDs)
kubectl apply -n argo-rollouts \
  -f https://github.com/argoproj/argo-rollouts/releases/latest/download/install.yaml

# Wait for pods
kubectl get pods -n argo-rollouts

# Then install Helm chart
helm install retail-release ./Retail-chart --namespace retail
```

